Gnome is installed with speach enabled by default.
In addition we enable autologin to prevent screen reader accesibility issues.

Additional information can be found here:

https://help.gnome.org/users/orca/stable/howto_the_orca_modifier.html.en

Some Keybind Information:

The screen reader application can be enabled or disabled with the keybind:
ALT + SUPER + S
